RUGANO RWA MTIGAIRI JOHN WAMBUGU THANDI  
GUCIARWO  
BIOGRAPHY OF THE LATE JOHN WAMBUGU THANDI  
BIRTH  
The late John Wambugu Thandi was born in the year 1954 in Gatitu village, Nyeri  
County. He was born to the late Wambugu Nduire and Grace Wangari. He was the  
second born in a family of six children, namely Mary Wangui, the late Alex  
Mwangi, the late David Maina, Simon Kariuki, and Daniel Theuri.  
Mutigaire John Wambugu Thandi aciariwo mwaka-ini wa 1954 itura-ini ria gatitu Nyeri ni  
aciari ake atigaire Wambugu nduire na Grace Wangari. Ari mwana wao wa keri  
maciaranirwo na mary Wangui, mutigaire Alex Mwangi, mutigaire David Maina, Simon  
Kariuki na Daniel Theuri  
KURERWO  
UPBRINGING  
The late John Wambugu Thandi was raised by his parents together with other  
children in Kongoni village, Naivasha. He helped his parents with various  
household and family responsibilities.  
Mutigaire John Wambugu Thandi arerirwo ni aciari ake ota ciana iria ingi itura-ini ria  
kongo-ini Naivasha, niateithageriria aciari ake mawira mamu cie  
GITHOMO  
EDUCATION  
Abiririe githomo mwaka-ini wa 1965 cukuru-ini wa Kongoni Primary School ginyagia  
1972.  
He began his primary education in 1965 at Kongoni Primary School and completed  
his studies in 1972.  
KUGIMARA  
CIRCUMCISION  
The late John Wambugu Thandi was circumcised in the year 1972.  
Mutigaire John Wambugu Thandi agimarire mwaka-ini wa 1972  
WIRA  
WORK  
Mutigaire John Wambugu Thandi ni athire mwena wa Nairobi mwaka-ini wa 1979 koria  
abiririe wira wake wa mechanic. No arari derefa Safari Park Hotel omwena ocio wa  
Nairobi  
In 1979, John Wambugu Thandi moved to Nairobi where he started working as a  
mechanic. Later, he worked as a driver at Safari Park Hotel in Nairobi.  
MARRIAGE  
KUHIKANIA  
John Wambugu Thandi married his beloved wife, Jecinta Njoki, in the year 1980.  
Their marriage was blessed with six children, Grace Wangari Wambugu, the late  
Wambugu, Eliud Mathu Wambugu, Eunice Wanjiku Wambugu, Samwel Iloku  
Wambugu, and the late Thandi.  
Mutigaire John Wambugu Thandi ni menduire no mwendwa wake Jecinta Njoki na  
makihikania mwaka-ini wa 1980 mwathani ni a matana heiri na ciana ithathato. Nicio  
Grace Wangari Wambugu, mutigaire Wambugu, Eliud Mathu Wambugu, Eunice Wanjiku  
Wambugu, Samwel Iloku Wambugu na Mutigaire Thandi  
CHURCH  
KANITHA  
John Wambugu Thandi was baptized at Revival Restoration Ministry Church in  
the year 2019.  
Mutigaire John Wambugu Thandi abatithirio kanithaini wa Revival Restoration Ministry  
mwaka-ini wa 2019  
ILLNESS AND DEATH  
NDWARI  
The late Wambugu was hospitalized for a period of one month following an  
illness. He passed away peacefully on the morning of 19 December 2025. He died  
at the age of 71. He has left his wife, four children, and seven grandchildren.  
Mtigaire Wambugu ni arakoretwo emuruaru kwa hinda na mweri uyo kuri mathaa ma  
hwaini 19/12/2025 Akehurukiu ni mwathani. Arahukire ena ukuru wa miaka 71(seventy-  
one) mutigairi atiga mutumia na ciana inya na tucucu mugwanja na gacukuru kamwe
